section.contributors-main
  .row
    .large-16.columns.contrubutors-title
      h2 Red Hat Developers Content Contributors
      h4 Share more. Learn more. Code More. 
    .large-8.columns.contributors-cta
      h5.caps Become a Content Contributor!
      p It’s easy to get started with 3 ways to contribute: General contributor, Most Valuable Contributor and Developers on the Street. 
      a.button href='signup' Sign Me Up!

section
  .row.contributers-sec1
    .large-24.columns
      h3 Welcome to Red Hat Developers Content Contributors
      br
    .large-10.columns
      p.text
        | Red Hat believes in and is founded on community.  Combining the community within Red Hat and outside of Red Hat makes the content better, more interesting, and frankly, makes us all smarter.
      p.text
        | You don’t have to consider yourself a great writer to participate. You can contribute what you have done, seen or tried.  Blogs, demos, videos, stories, conference experiences – they all provide value to the community.  It doesn’t have to be fancy, just authentic.
    .large-14.columns 
      .row.benefits
        .large-24.columns
          h4 There are many benefits to contributing!
        .large-8.small-24.columns
          span.left
            img(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/red_1.png"))
          span
            h6.caps Build your personal brand
          p Share your work with the world. Whether you want to be a blogger, present at conferences or set yourself up for your next role your brand is key.
        .large-8.small-24.columns
          span.left
            img(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/red_2.png"))
          span
            h6.caps Extend your reach
          p Let us put the power of our team behind your content and help you reach new audiences.
        .large-8.small-24.columns
          span.left
            img(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/red_3.png"))
          span
            h6.caps Get swag &amp; opportunities
          p Earn your way to great swag, the chance to get a free DevNation ticket or be invited to join our advisory board.

section.contributers-sec2
  .row
    .large-24.columns
      h2 Contributor Options
  .row
    .large-8.small-24.columns
      img(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/wc_icon.png"))
      h4 General Contributor
      p Contributes content once or twice a year
    .large-8.small-24.columns
      img(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/mvc_icon.png"))
      h4 Most Valuable Contributor (MVC)
      ul
        li Contributes semi-regularly
        li Earns points for swag with each contribution
        li Opportunity to earn free DevNation tickets
        li Potentially earn invitation to join the Red Hat Developers Content Advisory Board
    .large-8.small-24.columns
      img(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/dots_icon.png"))
      h4 Developer on the Street (DOTS)
      ul
        li Contributes recaps from conferences
        li Provides presentation decks to be shared (if relevant)
        li Earns swag
        li Submits short pieces about sessions, events or meet-ups

section.contributers-sec3
  .row
    .large-24.columns
      h2 It’s your choice!
      h2.caps WHICH OPTIONS ARE RIGHT FOR YOU?
    .large-12.columns
      p Wondering where to start as a contributor?  Get started finding your match by selecting one of the options below.  And the good news, you can switch between programs as your schedule allows.  No change request needed.
  
  .row
    form#contributorsQuiz
      .large-24.columns
        h3 How often would you like to contribute content?        
      .cc-selector
        .large-10.small-24.columns.cc-question
          input(id="q1a1" type="radio" name="Q1" value="q1a1")
          label(class="answer-cc radio-clock" for="q1a1") 
            div.label-text
              img.unchecked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/unchecked.png"))
              img.checked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/checked.png"))
              p I&#39;m interested in contributing semi-regularly and earning points for swag.
          
        .large-4.small-24.columns
          h2.cc-or or
        
        .large-10.small-24.columns.cc-question
          input(id="q1a2" type="radio" name="Q1" value="q1a2")
          label(class="answer-cc radio-calendar"for="q1a2")
            div.label-text
              img.unchecked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/unchecked.png"))
              img.checked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/checked.png"))
              p I&#39;m only interested in contributing once or twice a year.
      

      .large-24.columns
        h3 Do you attend conferences and meet-ups?
      .cc-selector
        .large-10.small-24.columns.cc-question
          input(id="q2a1" type="radio" name="Q2" value="q2a1")
          label(class="answer-cc radio-podium-woman" for="q2a1") 
            div.label-text
              img.unchecked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/unchecked.png"))
              img.checked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/checked.png"))
              p  I present at or attend conferences and meet-ups.
        
        .large-4.small-24.columns
          h2.cc-or or
        
        .large-10.small-24.columns.cc-question
          input(id="q2a2" type="radio" name="Q2" value="q2a2")
          label(class="answer-cc radio-podium-empty"for="q2a2")
            div.label-text
              img.unchecked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/unchecked.png"))
              img.checked(src=cdn("#{site.base_url}/images/content-contributors/checked.png"))
              p  I do not attend conferences and meet-ups.
  
    .large-24.columns
      .answer-block
        h3.result-title
        p.result-text
        a.button(href='signup') Sign Me Up!

section.contributers-sec4
  .row
    .large-10.columns
      h2 Have a question?
    .large-13.columns
      p 
        | If you have any additional questions about being a Red Hat Developers Content Contributor, you can
        a href="mailto:contributors@redhat.com"  email Emily
        |.

